_:N2a4c7f59a8c84b36b091ebcb7a0863d9 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Rebecca Harris was Government Whip (Lord Commissioner of HM Treasury) from 9 January 2018 to 5 July 2024. Rebecca was an Assistant Government Whip in the House of Commons from June 2017 to January 2018.</p>\n\n<p>She was elected Conservative MP for Castle Point in May 2010.</p>\n" .
